text: o visvasulara! Niscayanga, cala mandi yuda matacarulu (ah bar) mariyu kraistava san'yasulu (ruh ban) prajala sottunu akrama pad'dhatula dvara tini vestunnaru mariyu varini allah margam nundi atanka parustunnaru. Mariyu evaraite vendi, bangaranni kuda betti, danini allah marganlo kharcu pettaro variki badharakamaina siksa galadane vartanu vinipincu
